Anyone going from newark-jersey jersey-denver in the next week????????
**REPOST: If we can get this little guy on a flight from Newark, New Jersey to Denver, Colorado in the next week or so, I will gladly give him his forever home. 
For the past 11 years he has been forced to live in a cage and used for breeding in Puerto Rico.  He's never known the love and security and comfort of a real home. @strayfromtheheart has found him a flight from Puerto Rico to Newark NJ. Now we just need to get him to Denver. 
If you happen to be flying to Denver from Newark in the next several days and would allow this 4 lbs guy to fly with you in cabin, @strayfromtheheart will cover his flight costs, and arrangements will be made to meet you at the Denver airport. 
Please contact Marcela at Marcela.strayfromtheheart@gmail.com  if you can help. 
Adding another dog will be a challenge for me and my housekeeper and my roommate but knowing this little guy will have the home he needs for Christmas is worth every bit of extra work. 
His name is Kenny.
